\end{align*}

Now we add the results:

$$f(-2)+f(-1)+f(0)=\frac{2}{1}+\frac{5}{3}+1=\frac{6}{3}+\frac{5}{3}+\frac{3}{3}=\frac{14}{3}$$

The answer is $\boxed{\frac{14}{3}}$.

